template: SELECT MIN(link_type.id) AS link_type_id FROM movie_info, movie_link, movie_companies, title, link_type WHERE movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info.movie_id = title.id AND movie_link.movie_id = title.id AND link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id AND movie_companies.note NOT LIKE %s AND title.production_year < %s AND movie_info.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi') AND movie_info.note LIKE %s AND link_type.link LIKE %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000 AND title.episode_nr < %s;
